---
---
<section id="model-output" class="section">
  <div class="container">
    <div class="section-header text-center">
      <h2>Model <span class="text-gradient">Output</span></h2>
      <p class="section-subtitle">Understanding the diagnosis results from the classifier.</p>
    </div>
    
    <div class="grid-2-col">
      <div class="explanation-card glass-panel">
        <div class="card-icon">🧠</div>
        <h3>Intelligent Classification</h3>
        <p>The classifier returns the highest-scoring label from the model output. Labels follow a specific format such as <code class="code-badge">Crop___Disease</code> or <code class="code-badge">Crop___healthy</code>.</p>
        <p>The application seamlessly converts these raw technical labels into highly readable, user-friendly crop and disease names.</p>
        
        <div class="info-alert">
          <span class="alert-icon">ℹ️</span>
          <p><strong>Note:</strong> The current model is trained to recognize 68 distinct crop and condition combinations.</p>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="example-panel glass-panel">
        <h3>Example Diagnosis</h3>
        
        <div class="conversion-visual">
          <div class="label-box raw">
            <span class="label-type">Raw Label</span>
            <span class="label-value font-mono">Tomato___Late_blight</span>
          </div>
          
          <div class="conversion-arrow">
            <div class="arrow-line"></div>
            <div class="arrow-head"></div>
          </div>
          
          <div class="label-box processed">
            <span class="label-type">Displayed Result</span>
            <span class="label-value text-gradient font-bold">Tomato - Late blight</span>
          </div>
        </div>

        <div class="output-fields">
          <h4>Output Information</h4>
          <div class="fields-grid">
            <div class="field-item">
              <span class="check-icon">✓</span> Crop name
            </div>
            <div class="field-item">
              <span class="check-icon">✓</span> Disease/healthy status
            </div>
            <div class="field-item">
              <span class="check-icon">✓</span> Confidence score
            </div>
            <div class="field-item">
              <span class="check-icon">✓</span> Identified symptoms
            </div>
            <div class="field-item">
              <span class="check-icon">✓</span> Possible causes
            </div>
            <div class="field-item">
              <span class="check-icon">✓</span> Management guidance
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<style>
  .section-header {
    margin-bottom: var(--space-3xl);
  }
  
  .section-subtitle {
    font-size: var(--font-size-xl);
    color: var(--color-text-secondary);
  }

  .explanation-card, .example-panel {
    padding: var(--space-xl);
    height: 100%;
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
  }

  .card-icon {
    font-size: 3rem;
    margin-bottom: var(--space-m);
  }

  .explanation-card h3, .example-panel h3 {
    font-size: var(--font-size-2xl);
    margin-bottom: var(--space-m);
  }

  .explanation-card p {
    color: var(--color-text-secondary);
    margin-bottom: var(--space-m);
    line-height: 1.7;
  }

  .code-badge {
    background: rgba(16, 185, 129, 0.1);
    color: var(--color-brand-primary);
    padding: 0.2rem 0.5rem;
    border-radius: var(--radius-sm);
    font-family: monospace;
    border: 1px solid rgba(16, 185, 129, 0.2);
  }

  .info-alert {
    margin-top: auto;
    background: rgba(59, 130, 246, 0.1);
    border-left: 4px solid #3b82f6;
    padding: var(--space-m);
    border-radius: 0 var(--radius-md) var(--radius-md) 0;
    display: flex;
    gap: var(--space-s);
    align-items: flex-start;
  }

  .info-alert p {
    margin: 0;
    color: #93c5fd;
    font-size: var(--font-size-sm);
  }

  .conversion-visual {
    background: var(--color-bg-base);
    border-radius: var(--radius-lg);
    padding: var(--space-l);
    margin-bottom: var(--space-xl);
    border: 1px solid var(--color-border-subtle);
  }

  .label-box {
    padding: var(--space-m);
    border-radius: var(--radius-md);
    text-align: center;
    position: relative;
  }

  .label-box.raw {
    background: rgba(30, 41, 59, 0.8);
    border: 1px dashed var(--color-border-subtle);
  }

  .label-box.processed {
    background: rgba(16, 185, 129, 0.05);
    border: 1px solid rgba(16, 185, 129, 0.3);
    box-shadow: 0 0 20px rgba(16, 185, 129, 0.1);
  }

  .label-type {
    display: block;
    font-size: var(--font-size-xs);
    text-transform: uppercase;
    letter-spacing: 0.1em;
    color: var(--color-text-muted);
    margin-bottom: var(--space-xs);
  }

  .label-value {
    font-size: var(--font-size-lg);
    color: var(--color-text-primary);
  }

  .font-mono {
    font-family: monospace;
  }

  .font-bold {
    font-weight: 700;
  }

  .conversion-arrow {
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    align-items: center;
    height: 40px;
    justify-content: center;
    position: relative;
  }

  .arrow-line {
    width: 2px;
    height: 100%;
    background: linear-gradient(to bottom, var(--color-border-subtle), var(--color-brand-primary));
  }

  .arrow-head {
    width: 0;
    height: 0;
    border-left: 6px solid transparent;
    border-right: 6px solid transparent;
    border-top: 8px solid var(--color-brand-primary);
    position: absolute;
    bottom: -4px;
  }

  .output-fields h4 {
    color: var(--color-text-secondary);
    font-size: var(--font-size-sm);
    text-transform: uppercase;
    letter-spacing: 0.05em;
    margin-bottom: var(--space-m);
  }

  .fields-grid {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: 1fr;
    gap: var(--space-s);
  }

  @media (min-width: 480px) {
    .fields-grid {
      grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr;
    }
  }

  .field-item {
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    gap: var(--space-s);
    color: var(--color-text-secondary);
    font-size: var(--font-size-sm);
    padding: var(--space-s);
    background: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.02);
    border-radius: var(--radius-sm);
    transition: background 0.2s ease;
  }

  .field-item:hover {
    background: rgba(16, 185, 129, 0.05);
    color: var(--color-text-primary);
  }

  .check-icon {
    color: var(--color-brand-primary);
    font-weight: bold;
  }
</style>
